/-- The subfunctor of `F` obtained by restricting to the preimages of a set `s ‚àà F.obj i`. -/
@[simps] def to_preimages : J ‚•§ Type v :=
{ obj := Œª j, ‚ãÇ f : j ‚ü∂ i, F.map f ‚Åª¬π' s,
