  (F.to_eventual_ranges.map f).surjective :=
Œª ‚ü®x, hx‚ü©, by { obtain ‚ü®y, hy, rfl‚ü© := h.subset_image_eventual_range F f hx, exact ‚ü®‚ü®y, hy‚ü©, rfl‚ü© }

